ong)|Mrs. Potato Head]]\n| length12 = 3:37\n| writer12 = {{flatlist|* Martinez\n*Dussolliet\n*Sommers}}\n| extra12 = Kinetics & One Love\n| title13 = Mad Hatter\n| length13 = 3:21\n| writer13 = {{flatlist|* Martinez\n* Dussolliet\n* [[Frequency (record producer)|Bryan Fryzel]]\n* [[Aalias|Aaron Kleinstub]]}}\n| extra13 = {{flatlist|* Frequency\n* Aalias}}\n| total_length = 46:38\n}}\n{{Track listing\n| headline  = Digital deluxe edition<ref>{{cite web|url = https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/cry-baby-deluxe-edition/id1021871522|title = iTunes Store (US) \u2013 Music \u2013 Melanie Martinez \u2013 Cry Baby (deluxe edition)|access-date = June 2, 2016|date = August 14, 2015|work = [[iTunes Store]] (US)}}</ref>\n| extra_column  = Producer(s)\n| collapsed  = yes\n| total_length  = 56:01\n| title14  = Play Date\n| writer14  = {{flatlist|* Martinez\n* [[Jennifer Decilveo]]}}\n| extra14  = {{flatlist|* Keenan\n* Decilveo}}\n| length14  = 2:59\n| title15  = Teddy Bear\n| writer15  = {{flatlist|* Martinez\n* [[Phoebe Ryan]]\n* Felix Snow}}\n| extra15  = Snow\n| length15  = 4:05\n| title16  = Cake\n| writer16  = {{flatlist|* Martinez\n* Christopher Baran\n* DioGuardi}}\n| extra16  = CJ\n| length16  = 3:19\n}}\n'''Notes'''\n* {{ref|a|[a]}} signifies an additional producer.\n* \"Pity Party\" samples [[Lesley Gore]]'s \"[[It's My Party (Lesley Gore song)|It's My Party]]\", written by [[Wally Gold]], John Gluck, Herb Wiener, and Seymour Gottlieb.\n\n==Personnel==\n* [[Melanie Martinez]]&nbsp;\u2013 [[Singing|vocals]]&nbsp;\n'''Production'''\n* Jeff Levin \u2013 [[Artists and repertoire|A&R]]\n* [[Pete Ganbarg]]&nbsp;\u2013 A&R\n* Anne Declemente&nbsp;\u2013 A&R\n*Mitch McCarthy &nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]] on all tracks except \"Dollhouse\", \"Carousel\" and \"Pity Party\" at Owl Foot Ranch\n* [[Manny Marroquin]] &nbsp;\u2013 mixing on \"Pity Party\"\n* Chris Gehringer&nbsp;\u2013 [[Mastering (audio)|mastering]]\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n==