sts and repertoire|A&R]]\n* [[Pete Ganbarg]]&nbsp;\u2013 A&R\n* Anne Declemente&nbsp;\u2013 A&R\n*Mitch McCarthy &nbsp;\u2013 [[Audio mixing (recorded music)|mixing]] on all tracks except \"Dollhouse\", \"Carousel\" and \"Pity Party\" at Owl Foot Ranch\n* [[Manny Marroquin]] &nbsp;\u2013 mixing on \"Pity Party\"\n* Chris Gehringer&nbsp;\u2013 [[Mastering (audio)|mastering]]\n\n==Charts==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Weekly charts===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\"| Chart (2015\u201317)\n! scope=\"col\"| Peak<br /> position\n|-\n{{albumchart|Australia|27|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 22, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Flanders|77|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 21, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Wallonia|149|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 21, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|BillboardCanada|10|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|accessdate=August 24, 2015|refname=CANalbum|rowheader=true}}\n|-\n{{album chart|Croatia|24|id=1792|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 20, 2017}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Netherlands|65|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 21, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Finland|36|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=May 15, 2016}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Ireland|35|year=2015|week=34|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 21, 2015}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| Italian Albums ([[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana|FIMI]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fimi.it/classifiche#/category:album/id:2362|title=Album \u2013 Classifica settimanale WK 44 (dal 2016-10-28 al 2016-11-03)|publisher=[[Federazione Industria Musicale Italiana]]|language=Italian|accessdate=November 5, 2016}}</ref>\n| 18\n|-\n{{albumchart|New Zealand|21|artist=Melanie Martinez|album=Cry Baby|rowheader=true|accessdate=August 21, 2015}}\n|-\n{{albumchart|Portugal|23|artist=Melanie Martinez|al