ate=March 13, 2018}}</ref>}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United Kingdom|artist=Melanie Martinez|title=Cry Baby|award=Gold|type=album|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}\n{{Certification Table Entry|region=United States|artist=Melanie Martinez|title=Cry Baby|award=Platinum|type=album|certyear=2017|accessdate=March 2, 2017}}\n{{Certification Table Bottom|streaming=true}}\n\n==''Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP''==\n{{Infobox album\n| name         = Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP\n| type         = EP\n| artist       = [[Melanie Martinez]]\n| cover        = Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP Cover.jpg\n| border       = yes\n| alt          = \n| released     = November 25, 2016\n| recorded     = 2013\u20132015\n| venue        = \n| studio       = \n| genre        = \n| length       = 13:51\n| label        = [[Atlantic Records|Atlantic]]\n| producer     = \n| prev_title   = [[Pity Party (song)#Pity Party EP|Pity Party EP]]\n| prev_year    = 2016\n| next_title   = [[K-12 (album)|K-12]]\n| next_year    = 2019\n| misc         = {{Singles\n | name = Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP\n | type = ep\n | single1 = Gingerbread Man\n | single1date = August 1, 2015\n}}\n}}\n'''''Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP''''' is the third [[extended play]] by American recording artist [[Melanie Martinez]], released on November 25, 2016. The EP is a physical vinyl release of the three bonus tracks from ''Cry Baby'' as well as the limited-release 2015 [[Christmas]] single, \"Gingerbread Man\".<ref>{{Cite web|last=Grebey|first=James|url=https://www.spin.com/2015/12/melanie-martinez-gingerbread-man-stream/|title=Melanie Martinez Shares Sweet and Spicy New Track, 'Gingerbread Man'|date=2015-12-23|website=Spin|access-date=2019-06-12}}</ref><ref name=\"crybabyextra\">{{cite web|title=Cry Baby's Extra Clutter Vinyl EP|url=http://store.melaniemartinezmusic.com/cry-baby-s-extra-clutter-vinyl-ep.html|website=Melanie Martinez|accessdate=21 October 2016}}</ref> The vinyl was only available for purchase via [[Urban Outfitters]] and Martinez's website.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.urbanoutfitters.com/urban/catalog/productdetail.jsp?id=41175720&category=A-VINYL-NEW|title=Melanie Martinez - Cry Baby's Extra Clutter EP $14.98|last=|first=|date=2016|website=[[Urban Outfitters]]|publisher=|access-date=December 2, 2016}}</ref> The EP's cover art was drawn by Chloe Tersigni.\n\n===Track listing===\n{{Track listing\n| collapsed = no\n| headline = Vinyl\n| extra_column = Producer(s)\n| title1 = Play Date\n| note1 = \n| length1 = {{duration|m=2|s=59}}\n| writer1 = {{flatlist|\n* [[Jennifer Decilveo]]\n* [[Melanie Martinez]]\n}}\n| extra1 = {{flatlist|\n* Michael Keenan\n* [[Jennifer Decilveo]]\n}}\n| title2 = Teddy Bear\n| note2 = \n| length2 = {{duration|m=4|s=5}}\n| writer2 = {{flatlist|\n* Martinez\n* [[Phoebe Ryan]]\n* Felix Snow\n}}\n| extra2 = Snow\n| title3 = Cake\n| note3 = \n| length3 = {{duration|m=3|s=19}}\n| writer3 = {{flatlist|\n* Martinez\n* Baran\n}}\n| extra3 = Baran\n| title4 = Gingerbread Man\n| note4 = \n| length4 = {{duration|m=3|s=28}}\n| writer4 = {{flatlist|\n* Martinez\n* Keenan\n* Arthur McArthur\n}}\n| extra4 = {{flatlist|\n* Keenan\n* McArthur\n}}\n| total_length = 13:51\n}}\n\n{{clear}}\n\n==Tour==\n{{Unreferenced section|date=September 2019}}{{Infobox concert\n| artist        = [[Melanie Martinez]]\n| album         = '''''Cry Baby'''''\n| start_date    = August 26, 2015\n| end_date      = April 2, 2017\n| number_of_legs = 9\n| number_of_shows = 98 in North America<br />4 in Oceania<br />5 in Latin America<br />17 in Europe<br />124 in total\n| gross     =\n| last_tour = Dollhouse Tour<br />(2014\u201315)\n| this_tour = '''Cry Baby Tour'''<br />(2015\u201317)\n| next_tour = [[K-12 Tour]]<br />(2019-20)\n}}\n\n=== Set list ===\n{{div col}}\n# \"[[Cry Baby (Melanie Martinez song)|Cry Baby]]\"\n# \"[[Dollhouse (Melanie Martinez song)|Dollhouse]]\"\n# \"[[Sippy Cup (song)|Sippy Cup]]\"\n# \"[[Carousel (Melanie Martinez song)|Carousel]]\"\n# \"Alphabet Boy\"\n# \"[[Soap (Melanie 